OL,3,CPainting by Sir Winston Churchill to
OL,4,Cbe shown at family home for first time
OL,6,FA painting by wartime prime minister
OL,7,FSir Winston Churchill will go on
OL,8,Fdisplay in the UK for the first time
OL,9,Fat his former family home in Kent.
OL,11,F'Quiet Waters', showcasing a tranquil
OL,12,Flandscape, will feature alongside
OL,13,FChurchill's painting coat in an
OL,14,Fexhibition of his paintings and art
OL,15,Fmaterials, which opens at Chartwell on
OL,16,FSaturday (28 February).
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
