PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772197440
OL,3,CPainting by Sir Winston Churchill to
OL,4,Cbe shown at family home for first time
OL,6,F"It was his way of getting away from
OL,7,Fthe stresses and strains of public and
OL,8,Fpolitical life.
OL,10,F"At Chartwell, visitors can explore
OL,11,Fhow art became his antidote to
OL,12,Fpressure and frustration ` items like
OL,13,Fhis well-used coat for painting along
OL,14,Fwith works he created bring us closer
OL,15,Fto those quiet, creative moments away
OL,16,Ffrom the world."
OL,18,FAmong the exhibits will be Churchill's
OL,19,Fsteel-framed glasses and white cotton
OL,20,Fcoat which he wore while creating more
OL,21,Fthan 500 works of art.
OL,26,@xD@PO]
